720298f-a.title: Manhattan: Hamilton Fish Park - Swimming pool.
720298f-a.text:
Hamilton Fish Park: A westward view of the northern half of same, showing a new swimming pool (constructed by the W.P.A.). This is one of the many public pools planned by Park Commissioner Moses.

April 26, 1935.

P. L. Sperr.
